700321f-a.title: Bronx: 204th Street (East) - Grand Concourse
700321f-a.text:
225 E. 204th Street, north side, between Grand Woncourse
und Valentine Avenue, showing an old frame house standing below
the street grade. This house does not actually bear No. 225.
It stands 82 feet back of the street, directly behind a 3 story
brick building bearinn the above street number. Che view is north.
eastward from the elevated level of E. 2O4t Street.
N8y 5, 1938.
P.L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
